snippet.title: ONE ROOM - Prisoner's Dilemma (English Sub)
snippet.description:
Download AVAILABLE NOW! (Windows ) : https://zephi.itch.io/one-room-prisoners-dilemma
Mystery Visual Novel - Average gameplay: 30 minutes.
Translation time: 3 days.
Personal Ranking: 8/10 (loved the twist at the end, so good but so short.)
Music: There's copyright so this video is 100% free of ads from me to you guys.
But please do support the creator of the game instead if possible on the original website.
https://keidy.tistory.com/356

For a simple visual novel this is one of the few that got me interested, the art was pretty normal and it felt good enough for the game. I don't have much comment on it, but I still enjoyed it for how little it has.
💚Patreon for WIPs :https://www.patreon.com/Zephirum
🤎The Ko-fi channel! :https://ko-fi.com/zephirum 
💜Discord Server : https://discord.gg/vE9AMGAunS
